F1 Qualifying Predictor

F1 Qualifying PredictorPredict Formula 1 qualifying lap times using machine learning trained on 2019–2024 FastF1 data.
Features

Qualifying Prediction — Select any team, driver and circuit to get a predicted lap time and grid position
Team Intelligence — Historical performance trends by year, circuit type, and speed class
R&D Setup Simulator — Simulate high vs low downforce configurations across all circuits

Model Details

Algorithm: XGBoost Regressor
Features: 27 features covering driver/team identity, circuit DNA, weather, tyre setup, speed traps
Train/Test split: Time-based (train ≤2023, test 2024)
Target: Qualifying lap time in seconds